title: Speed Demon #1 (Amalgam Comics)
description:
Speed Demon #1

The cover art on this book is sweet. My favorite out of the 12.

April 1996

Amalgam Comics (Marvel/DC)

I have the first 12 issues of Amalgam Comics. I read that they came out with another

these.
